1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,000
How does your body keep itself at the perfect temperature?

2
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:06,800
It's called thermoregulation—a process vital for survival.

3
00:00:06,800 --> 00:00:10,000
But it's not just about sweating or shivering.

4
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:11,600
There’s so much more!

5
00:00:11,600 --> 00:00:16,400
Your body uses blood flow, hormones, and even behavior to maintain balance.

6
00:00:16,400 --> 00:00:22,000
Every choice, from what you wear to when you drink water, impacts this process.

7
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:25,600
And there's still so much we don’t fully understand!

8
00:00:25,600 --> 00:00:29,600
Want to dive deeper into the science of your body?

